| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3957 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: ef475104-73c9-5229-a041-f7e31acaee31"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
